          <text><![CDATA[<p><b>Uncovering Foreign Influence in the United States Act of 2018 </b></p> <p>This bill establishes additional disclosure requirements for certain tax-exempt organizations that receive foreign source contributions. The bill also imposes an excise tax on a U.S. person who fails to disclose a political contribution that is made on behalf of or funded by a person other than a U.S. person or bona fide resident of a U.S. possession. </p>]]></text>
